data.description: Incredible opportunity awaits in this vibrant Brooklyn location! This three-family house is a gem, with the first floor offering a chic 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom layout. The second and third floors boast spacious 3-bedroom residences, each with a full bathroom. Picture yourself surrounded by wall-to-wall hardwood flooring, basking in the glow of recessed lighting in every room and jetted tubs. Step into the massive backyard, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. Enjoy the functionality of well-equipped kitchens, seamlessly connected to expansive living and dining spaces. With a finished basement, independent meters, and a peaceful, quiet neighborhood, this property is the epitome of urban living at its finest. Don't miss out on this exceptional home near public transportation, shopping, schools, and parks! Initial showing is drive-by until an offer is accepted.
